    - Hello, this pop up displays the information the scriptableObject called DialogueTree
    - 'The script ConversationController, holds a list over all the dialogues an
      NPC can talk through. The scripts has methods for moving between the dialogues
      and adding new ones.  '
    - 'For example, you could have the dialogue change on the completion of a task. '
    - The ConversationController accepts both the Scriptable Object called DialogueTree
      and the deserialized JSON version. You can find examples of both in our folders.
    - The script called DialogueBoxController displayes the dialogueTrees, as you
      can see right in front of you.
    - 'It also is connected to the Text-to-speech service which will read the dialogue
      aloud. '
    - 'You can read more about this on the wiki '
